i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv2wgnium&h=42afd2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民質疑黃洋達<br />\n<img src=\"http://holland.pk/uldjvs93\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuldjvs93&h=327557a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲言論<br />\n<img src=\"http://holland.pk/ifj6hp8v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fifj6hp8v&h=6b2fb8fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃洋達在Facebook留言，｢今日繼續受審，隔岸觀火，心焦如焚。但旺角的戰士向來比我勇武，小弟一直受他們保護。只求大家都平安。｣<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聲稱自已因為出席法庭耹訊的關係，未能留在旺角。不過，有網民在黃洋達facebook質疑他是不是要24小時在法庭受審，為何他上完法庭後，沒有於旺角出現。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，至於人稱國師的陳雲，徒子徒孫在旺角勇武力抗，他亦繼續在facebook留言，「沒有堅強的香港人，我無法建國的」，「到時你們這些所謂香港本土人就是仆X奴隸，做雞做奴做足十八世」，他到底想表達什麼，大家就要參詳一下。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"843c280fedd7904e95f0f8f6894d6d4e4ca17277","tid":22180,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"Cv <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b696e58b3ed11c3be959d8c778b23905f552b2","tid":22180,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"又開私怨post煩唔煩d"},{"pid":"d6cec211a524cd5509fbb7b23ada24cb40c1eb48","tid":22180,"uid":30203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩好屌呀<br />\n過左去既 一人少句喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢自己拎嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d431c9e4aab1b09d3bafc353a9e1d5ef0be91fb5","tid":22180,"uid":11830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又開私怨post煩唔煩d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁諗開心d就繼續啦"},{"pid":"f6699fa4bdd57fd6ffeee5b00633e32b3b0dd97f","tid":22180,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"